Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.16,0:00:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on "Transformers Prime"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will only respond to the power of a Prime!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our sensors detected a second Iacon-locator beacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.02,0:00:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smokescreen chooses a vehicle mode with screaming double "38S" on the doors,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,making him an easy target.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be lying if I said I wasn't more than concerned about Jack's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Star Saber,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a legendary weapon forged by Solus Prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Decepticons now face our darkest hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am receiving a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.94,0:00:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.11,0:00:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha Trion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.53,0:00:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, lord Megatron.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I do not question the wisdom of our tactical retreat,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:01:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,know that I am fully prepared to lead the troops in a counterattack against the Autobots.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counterattack?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you failed to notice Optimus Prime
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cleave an entire mountain with a single blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.51,0:01:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the Star Saber in his possession,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my enemy can obliterate us all with a wave of his hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must find a way to tip the balance of power back in our favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.92,0:01:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we not also possess a powerful relic of the ancients?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed... the forge of Solus Prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is useless, except in the hand of a Prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I might wield that power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if I were to control such a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus, what is Alpha Trion saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish that I could meet you under better circumstances, Optimus Prime,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:02:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I fear that Iacon will not withstand the next Decepticon assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you speak to me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from across the ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are listening to this message,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I take solace that you now possess the Star Saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am certain that you have deduced how these Cybertronian relics and Decepticon weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,came to be found on such a remote world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, I transported them there,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not so much to keep them far from Megatron's hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but to ensure that they reach yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.66,0:03:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you may have long suspected,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Covenant of Primus records events of the future as well as the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My imperfect understanding of its runes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,affords me a shadowy glimpse of what is to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Covenant's pages foretold that you, Optimus Prime,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would journey to the small, but significant planet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there engage in a crucial chapter in the war against the Decepticons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know neither the nature of the battle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nor its outcome, I only hope that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these relics of the ancients will aid the Autobots in your time of need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of utmost importance,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a few moments,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will launch the last of the relics,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the most significant and powerful of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Easy, Optimus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}So, did Alpha try and ask about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}What was the message?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}It is paramount that we recover the final four Iacon relics...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Omega keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the regeneration of our home planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:04:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Earth's Moon is a barren rock, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Indeed, Dreadwing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}But the Moon is not our destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}A space bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Our very own,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,relocated here after the Autobots discovered its whereabouts on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dark side of the Moon is hidden from prying human eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and, more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,well out of the Autobots' reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Dreadwing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall travel to the one place in the galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which may provide us with a means of defeating Optimus Prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pack your gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back to Cybertron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hahahaha. Well, believe it now, Bumblebee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Civilization at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember oil baths?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing I'm gonna do planetside is soak for an entire solar cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hahaha. I can't wait to tell Miko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Optimus, keys open doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can they really revive an entire planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I am unfamiliar with the lore of these Omega keys,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha Trion knew many secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the ancients possessed technology
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that has long been lost to what we consider modern science.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The devastation to our home world is worse than I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse the Autobots to the pit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever their function,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this much is certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:07:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we cannot restore Cybertron without all four Omega keys in our possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means we can't afford to lose a single one to Megatron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four sets of coordinates from Alpha Trion remain encrypted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is logical to conclude that each corresponds to the location of one of the Omega keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must not waver until I decode them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future of our home world depends on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A tomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One known to contain the remains of Primes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me you're not averse to desecration.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is just that being in such a place evokes powerful emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,considering the fate of my twin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should delight in our purpose here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to exact our revenge of Skyquake
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and of all our fallen brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall require a more practical means of carrying such a blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel funny saying this, but
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I want to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew we'd ever get so used to our new home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I don't think I'd ever want to leave Miko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've made friends here, family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could always... text them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,been fighting for so long, I don't know if I can do anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go back into construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the ancients may breathe life back into Cybertron's core,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but our war-ravaged cities will surely require rebuilding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't make any travel plans just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have to locate these Omega keys and secure them before the 'Cons do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:08:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like that'll be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus has the Star Saber now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron's end is in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I can do it, lord Megatron,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you're certain that's what you really want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like nothing I've ever desired before, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall induce stasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I wish to bear witness
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as you attach my new appendage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Autobots, I have decoded the first set of the final four coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Divide into teams in the event
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I'm able to decode another before the first team returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on team one. Who's with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh. Ha ha ha ha hahaha. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At long last, the power of the Primes belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First one is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No locator beacon,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which means the relic's still buried
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,right about... there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The forge of Solus Prime
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,possesses the ability to create anything from raw material.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,said raw material would be a big hunk of Dark Energon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Arcee, I-I owe you an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never meant to endanger Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans squish easily. I get that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't just about Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Prime can't afford any casualties,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,human or bot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already lost two seasoned partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a rookie on my scorecard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elite guardsman's honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. You lost two partners?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have decoded the next set of Iacon coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work, Soundwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha. Nice of the humans to pile all these rocks on top of our relic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much spells things out, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Help me move this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ancient humans must have thought the Omega key was a gift from the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, in a sense, they weren't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The relic... now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two against one. We can take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratchet, ground bridge, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smokescreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What manner of treasure did Iacon send us this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would slice you in two right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I need you to deliver a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Optimus Prime that if he wants this relic,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he must come and claim it himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Smokescreen was just... gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like he turned to dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arcee, do not blame yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could just as easily have been you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:15:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I say we go claim a piece of Megatron's miserable, metal hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. We have already lost another one of our own today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not risk more lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given what Arcee witnessed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it stands to reason that Megatron now possesses might to equal the Star Saber,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which means only I have a chance of recovering the Omega key.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fate of Cybertron rests upon its retrieval.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether Megatron knows it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claim your prize, Optimus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the Allspark, Megatron.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I find it affords me certain advantages,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,such as the use of the Forge of Solus Prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My first creation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fashioned from the very blood of Unicron.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call it the Dark Star Saber...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,slayer of Primes, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last we take our rightful places, Optimus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As gods, wielding the power of the cosmos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.34,0:17:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am but a soldier, Megatron,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you are a prisoner of your own twisted delusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Dark Star Saber has tasted one spark tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It still thirsts for that of a Prime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so it ends, just as I envisioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with your head beside my new trophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finders keepers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smokescreen, fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratchet, ground bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Missed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Optimus, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those trinkets from Iacon will not save you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not when I now possess the power to tear this world apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smokescreen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Omega key number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... how? I mean, I saw you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, uh, decided to borrow the Phase shifter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wave from the blast hit me like a wrecking ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The impact must have activated the shifter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how long I was unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I made my way back outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus and Megatron were deep in an epic throwdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I waited for the right moment to make my move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, can I keep it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it is really working out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Signature weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got yours. Optimus lost his.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The balance of power shifted again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While he may have wielded the power of the ancients for only one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus does not require it to be the mightiest of warriors.
